metadata.name: Gundam of Futures Past
metadata.description: It was the year 2022. Earth as we know it was falling apart. The seasons were becoming more extreme while governments of different countries were at odds. With the advancement of technology accelerating at rapid pace, one group of individuals started to create man operated Gundam machines. With these, they were able to protect themselves and save others in war ravaged areas. With this technology, they became saviors for the people.
